metadata.name: It's Bizzy Baby #1
metadata.description: It's Bizzy Baby NFT is a 3333 genesis collection based on Jungle Bay Ape Club and built on music, community, and bring musicians opportunity in Web3. Holders will get a free mint to the Ragerz NFT, voting rights in the Bizzy Life DAO, premium artist submissions for Bizzy Life Records, discounted mints for future Bizzy Life Record NFTs, holders-only merch and IRL & Metaverse festival/show opportunities.
